{"tid":2433743,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"山下智久與𡃁模鬼混後即登記官網 疑早已決定離巢闖荷李活","createTime":"2021-03-05T05:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T09:59:38.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"39a53b61ced8eaf75baa536210013ef47a3819ff","tid":2433743,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T05:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZddWuR-DrEGv57bqZdr-oUOaK6I=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TYKUCIUE6ZGGVL4KF6DMYCZAJE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZddWuR-DrEGv57bqZdr-oUOaK6I%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTYKUCIUE6ZGGVL4KF6DMYCZAJE.jpg&h=4a0f1533&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n35歲前日本尊尼事務所男星山下智久去年8月7日被爆於7月30日搭上高校生模特兒愛子，並在酒後相約到高級酒店開房密會八小時，醜聞令山下形象受損。被事務所雪藏的山下於同年11月再次被日媒指他10月底已經離巢尊尼事務所，決意到外國發展。<br />\n<br />\n脫離尊尼後，山下於上月28日開設官網和fanclub網站「Club9」，並於同日在離巢後首次開IG直播，吸引大約12萬fans收看，人氣度完全沒受影響。不過，近日就有圈中人爆料，指山下的官網早於8月2日就已經登記網域名稱，亦即與愛子過夜後兩日。由於當時山下根本不知道自己會斷正，意味着他在醜聞被公開前已準備離巢。有網民留言寸爆山下因決定了退出事務所，才放肆與愛子鬼混。此外，山下去年12月返回日本，將於劇集《東大特訓班2》中客串。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JntMWIY1EDbHNQjNFvsAaVpae1k=/802x501/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2RVYMC735JHQFIYAKNAYA4BEIA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJntMWIY1EDbHNQjNFvsAaVpae1k%3D%2F802x501%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2RVYMC735JHQFIYAKNAYA4BEIA.jpg&h=4c2eec2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/frTQzldj4-dxDa1cp4Vbifxn1CA=/802x614/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/T2CVS4CUXRB4LB3VIDM726XTCE.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfrTQzldj4-dxDa1cp4Vbifxn1CA%3D%2F802x614%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FT2CVS4CUXRB4LB3VIDM726XTCE.JPG&h=1cddeb4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210305/IXC3R7IWHNCGTFQSOWGPGQLFI4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210305%2FIXC3R7IWHNCGTFQSOWGPGQLFI4%2F&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUs5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=7b898417\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210305%2FIXC3R7IWHNCGTFQSOWGPGQLFI4%2F&h=9296407a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210305/IXC3R7IWHNCGTFQSOWGPGQLFI4/</a>"},{"pid":"eb4faf06bdcf2a7eeb5b79cd09943abe295ed126","tid":2433743,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T05:43:17.000Z","msg":"25仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af0072997b9957fc79a1e582d5e26853780f51c","tid":2433743,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb4faf06bdcf2a7eeb5b79cd09943abe295ed126","tid":2433743,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T05:43:17.000Z","msg":"25仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-0